lor=#FFFFFF>Comment</font></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/beverquestersofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=raynn>Raynn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/17/01 1:33:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Loneless</span><hr size=1> Last night I was soloing gnolls in Highpass (I wasn't in a grouping mood!) <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   and a very kind lev 28 warrior, Loneless Fighter, of the Chosen of Norrath stopped to aid me with a rather difficult Champ.  He then proceeded to bandage me, and then sat with me for several hours bandaging, assisting with kills or just offering an encouraging word.  Even when I bought him bandages because he had used his last to heal me, he insisted on paying me back for them.<br>
I feel so lucky to have met such a kind soul and I can't help wondering what I did to deserve a guardian angel watching over me for a few hours at least <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
~Raynn <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/beverquestersofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=galadriaculravenni>Galadria Culravenni</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 328<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/17/01 1:57:18 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Loneless</span><hr size=1> Hehe... must have been your stunning beauty, undeniable charm and shining personality. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Or was it just that you were a helpless little elf? Hehe... <br>
<br>
Nah, I imagine you are right and he is simply one of those kind and generous souls we are all lucky enough to encounter once in a while. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Thanks for bringing him to our attention, hon. Bravo, Loneless!<br>
<br>
Galadria<br>
&quot;My joy is in Victus Fortis&quot;<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/ugladriellumenaura.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gladriel Lumenaura</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/17/01 2:29:42 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Loneless</span><hr size=1> I would imagine a combination of the two...I of course do not include the 'helpless elf' explanation...and can't imagine anyone but Galadria with the guts to place this term anywhere near Raynn.<br>
<br>
I'll look out for him as I shall be heading back to High Keep soon. I'd also be happy to offer you what help I can Raynn if our game time coincides, but I'm afraid it won't be the same as the assistance of a shining warrior. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Gladriel Lumenaura <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uraloth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raloth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br>  Posts: 612<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/17/01 3:37:46 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.canadiancommentary.com/head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Loneless</span><hr size=1> Sounds like a great person indeed!  I always love meeting people like this - <br>
<br>
*fondly remembers Thoran's kindness to all in SK* <br>
<br>
They make the game that much better.<br>
<br>
Raloth <p><img src=http://www.canadiancommentary.com/everquest/images/ralothsig2.JPG></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/beverquestersofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=galadriaculravenni>Galadria Culravenni</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 332<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/18/01 9:09:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Loneless</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Actually the &quot;helpless little elf&quot; phrase was Raynn's - she was looking over my shoulder while I was posting! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Hehe... for some reason last night she kept getting the treatment again from all and sundry who passed through Highpass. Sometimes when she was in a group, someone would come by and buff HER and not the other members! Helpless little elf indeed. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
This is NOT of course, to take anything away from Loneless or the others who did in fact assist her out of the goodness of their hearts... There is sometimes just something about a player, or his or her attitude, that makes others more willing to stop and help or cast random buffs on the way through. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Maybe it is the fact that she appreciates it and always says thank you...<br>
<br>
Galadria<br>
&quot;My joy is in Victus Fortis&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/beverquestersofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=raynn>Raynn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/21/01 3:09:49 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Loneless</span><hr size=1> Hmmm Im starting to believe that boredom and kindness go hand in hand.. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   It seems the motivation for many kind acts I have recieved is &quot;well, its late and there are no good groups in the keep&quot; or &quot;Im waiting to get into a group&quot;.... <br>
     Not to take away, of course, from the good feeling it gives to help another without being asked, or to be helped without asking <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Merely an observation!<br>
~Raynn <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm18.showMessage?topicID=40.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm18.showMessage?topicID=36.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm18.emailToFriend?topicID=35.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm18.threadControl?topicID=35.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm18.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=35.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub44.ezboard.com/feverquestersofnorrathfrm18.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=35.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub44.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="everquestersofnorrathfrm20">General Forum<option value="everquestersofnorrathfrm16">Gatherings of the Brave<option value="everquestersofnorrathfrm25">Bazaar of the Brave<option value="everquestersofnorrathfrm17">Tales and Roleplay<option value="everquestersofnorrathfrm15">Questing<option value="everquestersofnorrathfrm18">Honour Role <option value="everquestersofnorrathfrm19">Dishonourable Denizens<option value="everquestersofnorrath